org.apache.derby.catalog

Interface AliasInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregateAliasInfo, MethodAliasInfo, RoutineAliasInfo, SynonymAliasInfo, UDTAliasInfo

    public interface AliasInfo
    An interface for describing an alias in Derby systems. In a Derby system, an alias can be one of the following:
    • method alias
    • UDT alias
    • class alias
    • synonym
    • user-defined aggregate
